Add Folder Sharing Functionality to Transcription Shares Module

- Introduced endpoints in TranscriptionSharesController for sharing, unsharing, and listing users with whom folders are shared.
- Enhanced TranscriptionSharesService to manage folder sharing logic, including access checks and recursive folder visibility.
- Created TranscriptionFolderSharedWith entity to track folder sharing relationships.
- Updated DTOs to include ShareFolderWithUserDto for sharing folder data.
- Modified TranscriptionsService to incorporate folder sharing checks in transcription visibility logic, improving user experience in accessing shared content.
